(3,'Refine the subject\'s hair to pixie cut, embracing the dark brown hair color for a striking appearance. Enhance the hair\'s richness and depth while maintaining a chic and polished look. Keep a smooth texture with slight waves for versatility. Maintain a casual aesthetic with easy maintenance and playful style. Strike a balance with moderate volume, allowing the hair to lay relatively flat with some lift for dimension. Maintain uniform dark brown color for cohesion. Style the hair forward with no visible parting to preserve its natural flow and movement. Use minimal styling techniques to ensure the natural texture remains prominent. No accessories needed to highlight the pixie cut. Integrate modifications realistically to capture the subject\'s bold and playful style accurately.','04b4c4b7-3dc2-48ec-baca-6b4d22a9e5e8.png','Curly Pixie Hairstyle','2024-04-11 22:27:29'),
