(4,'be6ddd39-6cc2-47ee-a659-95ffe16d65b2',1,'','\"Edit the person in the image to have no visible hair on their head. Ensure the new look is natural and matches their overall appearance seamlessly. This adjustment should make it appear as though they naturally have no hair on their head.\"',0,1,1,0,0,'2024-04-08 22:43:03'),
