(7,'b8962fd3-cb1c-4e7a-b521-06ca3c08f6ad',1,'','\"Alter the image in order to change the hair of the individual in the photo to reflect a bowl cut, which is a short haircut where the hair is cut straight around the head so that it resembles the shape of a bowl. The color should transition to a natural blonde, meticulously respecting the strands\' highlights and strokes, giving an intense and vibrant hue. The hair\'s texture should appear straight, achieved by the straightening of each individual strand to portray a silky smooth finish. Ensure a high volume, suggesting a full and thick look to the hair that adds an impression of density and robustness. You are to incorporate subtle highlights of a purple hue, accentuating the blonde base to create dimension and movement. Despite these changes, the overall context should still fit a formal setting depicting the hair as neat and well-groomed. Please keep the changes realistic and proportionate, integrating them flawlessly into the existing image as if they are naturally occurring.\"',0,5,2,0,0,'2024-04-08 22:50:08'),
(8,'b38a29a5-e37f-4fde-8124-03a80270965d',1,'','\"Alter the image to depict the subject\'s hair with a voluminous vintage bowl cut. The bowl cut should be textured, a technique that creates more dimension and depth by inducing an uneven, slightly rough pattern in straight hair. The molded haircut should be blonde, a soft, light hue, traditionally associated with warmth and luminosity. Integrate pink highlights subtly throughout the hair, providing gentle contrast and depth to the overall blonde color. The vintage tone suggests that the hairstyle should echo styles from past decades. It is critically important for the integration to be seamless and the final image to maintain a high degree of realism, as if the subject originally had this specific hairstyle and color combination. \"',0,4,2,0,0,'2024-04-08 22:54:02'),
(9,'88e6db7d-2d2b-4b6a-af85-ac23831342cc',1,'','Transform the subject\'s hair in the image to have a teal color representing a medium to dark greenish-blue, similar to the color of tropical oceans. The haircut should be a bob, a short to medium-length haircut, in which the hair is typically cut straight around the head at about jaw-level. Introduce a wavy texture to the hair, adding curves and soft peaks rather than straight strands. In the context of a formal event, the hair should be well styled, refined, and elegant. Ensure it\'s full-bodied with high volume, adding extra thickness and bounce to the hair. Introduce teal highlights for added dimension and visual interest. Finally, apply a straightening technique, which involves the use of heat or chemicals to remove the natural curls or waves in the hair, to give the hair a straighter texture. Please take note to ensure realistic integration of these changes to the hair as if they were applied in a professional salon setting.',0,3,1,0,0,'2024-04-08 22:58:46'),
(10,'30ff2657-9e4e-45e7-b727-ff697f4ca88b',1,'','\"Alter the original hairstyle in the image to a unique teal-colored mohawk style. Ensure the hair is straight, which means it has no wave or curl and falls flat. Despite the avant-garde hairdo, maintain a formal context which may invovle strategically styled side hair to complement the striking mohawk. Anticipate a level of disorderliness in the hair arrangement, drawing from the messy styling technique, imparting a touch of playful nonchalance to the otherwise formal and straight style. Note that the final product must visually integrate seamlessly into the image, appearing thoroughly realistic and natural as if the subject presented in the image originally possesses this striking hairstyle.\"',0,3,1,0,0,'2024-04-08 23:01:42'),
(11,'28afb2d9-0bfa-4db7-9b56-72024c2f0c6c',1,',,','Edit the current image by changing the hair color to a natural-looking blonde. The haircut should be adjusted to resemble a Bob style: a short, straight cut that levels with the jaw and typically comes with bangs or a fringe at the front. The hair\'s texture should remain the same as in the original image, undeniably maintaining its current form and quality. While applying these modifications, it is essential to ensure that the transformation is as seamless and realistic as possible, preserving the integrity of the image while making the hair appear as if it was originally blonde with a Bob haircut.',0,4,1,0,0,'2024-04-09 17:50:44'),
